com.facebook.buck.android

Class AndroidLibraryCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.android.AndroidLibraryCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImplicitDepsInferringDescription<AndroidLibraryDescription.Arg>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaAndroidLibraryCompiler, KotlinAndroidLibraryCompiler, ScalaAndroidLibraryCompiler

    public abstract class AndroidLibraryCompiler
extends Object
implements ImplicitDepsInferringDescription<AndroidLibraryDescription.Arg>
    Jvm compiler abstraction for android. Implementations of this class are used in AndroidLibraryDescription to provide the actual compilation step. This allows us to use different compilers for different AndroidLibraryDescription.JvmLanguage.
